name: Kitty Collector Fish - Cats Are Cute In The Bubble
name_original: Kitty Collector Fish - Cats Are Cute In The Bubble
description:
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Kitty.Collector.Fish.Cats.Are.Cute.Bubble.Berneons.Games.Free

Kitty Fish Collector - a game about a cute cat who collects fish in a soap ball to please the family of little kittens.

Features:
★ Collect the fish
★ Dodge the birds
★ Collect coins with bonuses
★ Call the tornado of fish
★ Feed the cat
★ Customize your cat
★ Buy cat hats
★ Collect cats
★ Cool effects of cats
